Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:13.50,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}{\pos(960,480)}All Arrangement, Lyrics, Composition: Revo\NVocals（演唱）: 香西愛美(Ami Kouzai)\NNarration（念白）: Ike Nelson\NStrings（弦乐）: 弦一彻弦乐团(Ittetsu Gen Strings)\NGuitars（吉他）: 西山毅(Takeshi Nishiyama), 大橋英之(Hideyuki Ouhashi)\NBass（贝斯，低音提琴）: 長谷川淳(Atsushi Hasegawa), 一本茂樹(Shigeki Ippon)\N（本场次所有曲目信息均引自Kaido）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:14.94,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}薄暮之下，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.94,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}冬日寒風，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.39,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}少女的身影。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:21.04,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}序幕，便於突然間開啟。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:24.50,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}回過神來...  已邁步奔去...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.43,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}心緒依售...  飄搖不定...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:31.83,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}遠去的...  白色高牆...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:36.05,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}一次...  也未曾反顧...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:39.54,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}《生命》...   逐漸流逝的季節...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.37,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}痛徹心扉的...氣息之中...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:46.79,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}暗影...  在逼近...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:50.85,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}仿佛再也...  不會迎來黎明...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:54.57,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}岌岌可危的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:57.54,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}仍拼命將其挽留...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:02.25,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}通往星空的漫長坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:07.81,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}仿佛...  便是永恒...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:11.57,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}繁花盛放...  亦終須散落...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:15.03,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}神之《代》起便周而復始...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:22.08,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}那是...  何等美....  我從未如此覺得...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:26.45,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}天長地久的...  春日暖陽...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:29.99,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}虛幻之影在彼此爭奪...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:37.50,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}那行徑是...  何等美景...  我從未如此覺得...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:41.23,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}如行屍走肉般...  生存於世...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:45.74,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}不再有任何奢望...  然而...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:49.39,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}還未放棄那...  最後的祈願...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.12,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}仍緊握在手...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.92,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}衡上那坡道...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.92,my_font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100, 100)}
